
Make sure you have:

- A C++ compiler that supports C++11 (e.g. gcc 4.6)
- CMake 2.8
- Boost 1.46
- SFML 2.0
- SQLite 3
- LuaJIT or Lua 5.1
- LuaBind
- Crypto++
- ENet 1.3
- OpenGL libraries
- Doxygen 1.8 (optional)


Build everything:

$ mkdir build
$ cd build
$ cmake ..
$ make
$ sudo make install


Start a server:

$ hexahedra-server


Start a client:

$ hexahedra

